      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning enthusiast is this E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled for precise cam timing. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a functional M-variable differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. While the finish shows minor stone chips and light interior bolster wear, the mechanical integrity is excellent. The suspension geometry remains tight with recent bushing replacements, ensuring the signature communicative steering feel this chassis is known for. A true driver-spec example that prioritizes longitudinal and lateral performance.",
